# BlueCore Alert Engine — Environment Configuration

```bash
ALERT_ENGINE_HOST=0.0.0.0
ALERT_ENGINE_PORT=8060
ALERT_DB_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://bluecore:bluecore@postgres:5432/alert_db
JWT_SECRET=change-me
REDIS_URL=redis://redis:6379/1
EVENT_BACKEND=kafka
KAFKA_BOOTSTRAP_SERVERS=kafka:9092
KAFKA_INGRESS_TOPIC=bluecore.alerts.ingress
KAFKA_PROCESSED_TOPIC=bluecore.alerts.processed
EVENT_STREAM_PREFIX=bluecore.alerts
OPENSEARCH_URL=
NEO4J_URI=
WEBSOCKET_GATEWAY_URL=http://websocket-gateway:8061
```
